What you need to know:

A field of 130 players, including invited guests, are drawn to battle it out this weekend for a number of prizes in various categories in the two-day eventAway in Nyeri, a field of 150, including 20 professionals will tackle the hilly Nyeri Golf Club course during the annual Benjamin Ndegwa Memorial golf tournamentThe par-72 Machakos Golf Club will this weekend host the Kitengela and Athi River Musketeers golf tournament